_sText:
Returning back to probably my favorite bhop series I've done so far.

Unlike the previous installments this map is linear. I mainly did this because I felt giving it checkpoints kind of limited the gameplay, and it just makes it flow better in my opinion.

Just so it's clear the red carpet on the 4th stage marks the end. The teleporter sends you to the bonus.

Sorry for the video being so pixelated. I have been working on improving the quality.
